<plot>Otto Feldman is obsessed with keeping everything in its place - down to the contents of his refrigerator. So when Otto gets fired from the family business, his entire life gets thrown into disarray. Taking the advice of his persistent neighbor Shinui Chaim, Otto attempts to win back his job and his piece of mind. But how far will Otto go to bring back stability in his life? Irreversible is a time-bending, thought-provoking thriller that like Otto, tries to put itself back where it started. But is it possible to restore balance without making a major change?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?268718</url></doc>
